* From the name of the {{m-lite|en|Gallaeci}}, a {{der|en|cel|-}} tribe of Iberia.
* From Latin {{m-lite|la|calidus||warm}}.
* From {{der|en|grc|Καλλίς||Beautiful}}, referring to the [[Douro]] valley; see {{m|grc|καλός||beautiful}}.
* An {{der-lite|en|xib|-}} pronunciation of {{cog|grc|Γαῖα||goddess of the Earth}}.

